 584:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal.c ****       (+) Enable/Disable the Voltage reference buffer
 585:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal.c **** 
